{"id": 3044, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你都会通过哪种方式“读”一本书？", "description": "对待不同的书籍，我有不同的阅读方式。（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ enisaksoy）", "record_count": 3805, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201910302310025aP16vswtmRJWLjO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-30T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5998, "title": "现如今你都会通过哪种方式“读”一本书？", "content": "现如今你都会通过哪种方式“读”完一本书？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349033, "content": "听书，放在音频 app 里每天听一点", "image": "img/option/option/201910302211321tqvPa2p9j8ZOGFi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349034, "content": "直接读豆瓣/微博上的书评，原文可以缓一缓再看", "image": "img/option/option/201910302217146DBQE1VtWRfdpvLq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349035, "content": "买这本书的知识付费版，相当于有人帮划重点", "image": "img/option/option/20191030222031K7XWYGpbmE5HNj4u.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349036, "content": "先从精读版/图解版看起，再考虑要不要入手原版", "image": "img/option/option/20191030222155vfBrSpVQqIdUAJNs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349037, "content": "参加线上或线下读书会，同时认识一本书和它的作者", "image": "img/option/option/20191030224224LIc4q6ETKO2u5ePZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349038, "content": "关注读书类公众号，每本都只看一点儿书摘", "image": "img/option/option/201910302252317xlUq3fzNdiBGTRX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349039, "content": "先看影视化版本建立起印象，再回过头找原著来读", "image": "img/option/option/20191030225621MUZAguoYdqhle1Oc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349041, "content": "放书架上供着，日积月累收获一种已经看过的错觉", "image": "img/option/option/20191030231635Rv4gX1tcUAI95ped.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349040, "content": "都不是，还是喜欢一页页读完（不管是纸书 or 电子书", "image": "img/option/option/20191030225805s1HCeDRQXKVF5zlr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}